Subject: How to Get (and Keep) a Tech Job
Description: To get a professional job, you must be adept at phone and Skype screening interviews. Once you get a job, you might be expected to program for 3 browsers plus Android and IOS devices, flawlessly. Or as a tester, you'll want to know mobile testing tools plus the Agile environment. We'll talk about all this, and more!  Speakers include:Donald Mark Haynes, Douglas Johnson - Track: Tech, Life  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: Projector
